{"h72135e50gfa93g4a96gb460g7f98b259f5dc": ["Amazing. She actually believed we'd take the poison.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "ee11a754-0017-63d8-e473-0ed99ce3a84a"], "h75e74549g0a49g432ega1aeg9d09abc32e1c": ["I'd rather die by my own hand than turn into one of those things.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "dff77d22-9979-6288-a6a9-ea187d4a00a4"], "hfb2fa3aage08eg4058gb75bgf2c2d77e76d6": ["Really? <i>Really?</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "9fc03f93-23f6-8948-cd7c-937ba58a238e"], "h9ac5d605gb0a1g4673g82ccg959b557e29e4": ["Well. Your funeral.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "5ea94ee3-8c32-fecd-65bf-326ffd11657e"], "hfcb83991g38a4g48bega4d4gc411b95755f7": ["And with that merry song in our hearts - let's go find this Halsin fellow.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "d2e53a22-8962-64c0-0cd1-17ebe483aa9c"], "hc71d6ba9gab98g4728g8898g45ec225bdade": ["It won't come to that. I'm not going to transform.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "b5f28f2c-7f6b-53d4-2356-f96b5bfcadd7"], "h22a6c36bg9e48g4820g9737ge5f5bd0321dc": ["Of course not, darling.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "1bf01b62-6146-4993-2070-aad52b5350aa"], "heda93ac5g5323g43c1gac8egcc8579c44b3c": ["The goblins will probably kill us long before that.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "c48019ae-f63e-d719-5194-e18dbf5da42a"], "h5f610c2dga0aeg49eeg8ebbg55dca0ffe2bc": ["People will believe anything that makes them feel better.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "aabf0683-5d9c-5891-3916-bb35f46cd42f"], "h6f309a03gd449g45cbgbe58g9801d30157a2": ["Well said. Let's drop that vial down the next well we find.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "d263173b-e377-8a0a-e827-ceddf1bdd73f"], "h805499efg23d0g432fgaf62g3bee599eecd1": ["Nicely done. She actually believed you'd take the poison.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\DEN_Apprentice_RD_Cyanide_Astarion.html", "4af86fd5-c046-356a-2cac-8feb1e5fd17f"]}